{"type":"message","id":"53f50ccd","parentId":"6a13cb8e","timestamp":"2026-05-08T19:25:13.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found it! The setting `interim_assistant_messages: true` is what controls whether process messages are deleted after the final response. But Hermes might have `interim_assistant_messages` set to `true` which means it KEEPS interim messages instead of deleting them.\n\nAlso `streaming: false` is interesting - Hermes might have streaming disabled.\n\nLet me check what the current settings are in Hermes config specifically, and also check what OpenClaw's default behavior is.\n\nThe key setting seems to be `interim_assistant_messages` - if true, it keeps them; if false, it deletes them.\n","thinkingSignature":"695b65350209d65e7da09127394e2e5fe2e929ea784d7d384e1f00148a8e8413"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i16nj6yc966u_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A 30 \"^telegram:\" ~/.hermes/config.yaml | head -40"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i16nj6yc966u_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -i \"interim_assistant_messages\\|streaming\\|tool_preview_length\" ~/.hermes/config.yaml"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":403,"output":206,"cacheRead":46336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46945,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778268307967,"responseId":"064d6b95955636573ea97354f95e2c36"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc6137d3","parentId":"53f50ccd","timestamp":"2026-05-08T19:25:14.048Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i16nj6yc966u_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"telegram:\n  reactions: false\n  channel_prompts:\n    '1060942816': สำหรับงานเขียนโค้ด แก้บั๊ก อ่าน/ค้น/วิเคราะห์โปรเจกต์ หรือคำถามเกี่ยวกับ\n      codebase ให้ใช้ SocratiCode MCP tools ก่อนเสมอเมื่อเกี่ยวข้อง โดยเฉพาะเครื่องมือชื่อ\n      socraticode/*; ถ้า SocratiCode ไม่รองรับ method ใด ให้ fallback ไปใช้ file/terminal\n      tools ปกติและบอกสั้น ๆ ว่า fallback แล้ว ห้ามปล่อยให้ error ของ SocratiCode\n      ทำให้ gateway หยุดทำงานหรือวน restart.\nslack:\n  channel_prompts: {}\nmattermost:\n  channel_prompts: {}\napprovals:\n  mode: manual\n  timeout: 60\n  cron_mode: deny\n  mcp_reload_confirm: true\ncommand_allowlist:\n- pipe remote content to shell\n- overwrite system file via tee\n- stop/restart system service\n- disk copy\n- overwrite system config\n- overwrite system file via redirection\n- hermes update (restarts gateway, kills running agents)\n- shell command via -c/-lc flag\n- overwrite project env/config file\n- recursive delete\n- delete in root path\n- script execution via -e/-c flag\n- script execution via heredoc"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":29,"aggregated":"telegram:\n  reactions: false\n  channel_prompts:\n    '1060942816': สำหรับงานเขียนโค้ด แก้บั๊ก อ่าน/ค้น/วิเคราะห์โปรเจกต์ หรือคำถามเกี่ยวกับ\n      codebase ให้ใช้ SocratiCode MCP tools ก่อนเสมอเมื่อเกี่ยวข้อง โดยเฉพาะเครื่องมือชื่อ\n      socraticode/*; ถ้า SocratiCode ไม่รองรับ method ใด ให้ fallback ไปใช้ file/terminal\n      tools ปกติและบอกสั้น ๆ ว่า fallback แล้ว ห้ามปล่อยให้ error ของ SocratiCode\n      ทำให้ gateway หยุดทำงานหรือวน restart.\nslack:\n  channel_prompts: {}\nmattermost:\n  channel_prompts: {}\napprovals:\n  mode: manual\n  timeout: 60\n  cron_mode: deny\n  mcp_reload_confirm: true\ncommand_allowlist:\n- pipe remote content to shell\n- overwrite system file via tee\n- stop/restart system service\n- disk copy\n- overwrite system config\n- overwrite system file via redirection\n- hermes update (restarts gateway, kills running agents)\n- shell command via -c/-lc flag\n- overwrite project env/config file\n- recursive delete\n- delete in root path\n- script execution via -e/-c flag\n- script execution via heredoc","cwd":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778268314048}}
